      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in pristine condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Vanos system to deliver a linear 8,000 RPM powerband. Mechanically optimized: the dual-VANOS has been overhauled with Beisan components, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a factory variable M-differential lock. The chassis exhibits zero fatigue, and the suspension retains its original factory-spec damping and bushing integrity. This is a collector-tier example with a documented service history and flawless paint depth.",
